import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; const Power = ({ currentLoad, capacity, motorData, jointData, labLoadData }) => { const [showMore, setShowMore] = useState(false); const [fluctuatingData, setFluctuatingData] = useState({}); const toggleMenu = () => { setShowMore(!showMore); }; useEffect(() => { const interval = setInterval(() => { // Generate random fluctuation in the range of -0.2 to 0.2 const fluctuation = (Math.random() - 0.5) * 0.4; // Update motorData setFluctuatingData(prevData => ({ ...prevData, motorData: { ...prevData.motorData, // Ensure that the value stays within the range [0, 1] frLoad: Math.max(0, Math.min(1, prevData.motorData.frLoad + fluctuation)), flLoad: Math.max(0, Math.min(1, prevData.motorData.flLoad + fluctuation)), brLoad: Math.max(0, Math.min(1, prevData.motorData.brLoad + fluctuation)), blLoad: Math.max(0, Math.min(1, prevData.motorData.blLoad + fluctuation)) }, // Update jointData jointData: { ...prevData.jointData, // Ensure that the value stays within the range [0, 1] j0Load: Math.max(0, Math.min(1, prevData.jointData.j0Load + fluctuation)), j1Load: Math.max(0, Math.min(1, prevData.jointData.j1Load + fluctuation)), j2Load: Math.max(0, Math.min(1, prevData.jointData.j2Load + fluctuation)), j3Load: Math.max(0, Math.min(1, prevData.jointData.j3Load + fluctuation)), j4Load: Math.max(0, Math.min(1, prevData.jointData.j4Load + fluctuation)), eeLoad: Math.max(0, Math.min(1, prevData.jointData.eeLoad + fluctuation)) }, // Update labLoadData labLoadData: { ...prevData.labLoadData, // Ensure that the value stays within the range [0, 1] x: Math.max(0, Math.min(1, prevData.labLoadData.x + fluctuation)), y: Math.max(0, Math.min(1, prevData.labLoadData.y + fluctuation)), z: Math.max(0, Math.min(1, prevData.labLoadData.z + fluctuation)), tray: Math.max(0, Math.min(1, prevData.labLoadData.tray + fluctuation)), gripper: Math.max(0, Math.min(1, prevData.labLoadData.gripper + fluctuation)) } })); }, 1000); // Repeat every second return () => clearInterval(interval); // Cleanup on unmount }, []); // Run effect only once after initial render return (
